title: Apple gives iPhone 6s Plus camera a test drive at New York Fashion Week
text: Apple’s new iPhone 6s and 6s Plus won’t officially arrive for customers until September 25th, but Apple is giving the upgraded camera on the devices a real world test drive at New York Fashion Week.
